[Student "S"]
{SOUTH has interest in slam after she hears NORTH's Limit Raise. 
BUT, she should not use Blackwood holding two quick losers in the \D 
suit.

Instead she makes a Control showing bid of 4\C. (Not Gerber since it didn't follow a NT bid.)

NORTH cooperates by making a Control bid of 4\H.

SOUTH stops at 4\S because neither partner controls \Ds.}

